name: DynamicPack For Snowboard「单板滑雪专用DynamicPack」

description: 「您可以使用这些浮动的嵌合体，unc0ver，sileo或cydia图标替换系统的动态墙纸。」You can replace the dynamic wallpaper of the system with these floating chimera, unc0ver, sileo or cydia icons. Just work with Snowboard extensions for now!
